      "content": "exactly. and it feels intentional, like it's not just some glitch or random bot. it's like there's a specific version of me being curated to change how people see me. if the AI is already doing this perfectly, how do i even prove it's not me? is there any way to stop it once the \"ghost\" starts acting on its own? like, once it has my voice, isn't it basically me now?",
